Quote: Government acted thus, because after making a count they found that the publicans had more noses in the House than the teetotallers; and the object of the New Zealand Alliance for the Reform of the liquor laws was to let Mr Sheehan and those of his sort see that the teetotallers had as many noses in the House as the publicans.
